column2: select yearId as year, playerId, sum(hr) as numHR   from baseball.batting   group by yearId, playerId ), hrs_ranked as ( select year, playerId, numHr   ,      rank() over (partition by year order by numHR desc) as rank   from hrs ) select hr.year, p.nameFirst, p.nameLast , hr.numHr, hr.rank   from hrs_ranked hr   join baseball.players p on p.playerid=hr.playerid  where hr.rank <=#  order by hr.year desc, hr.rank
